left class=m><span class=title> Temple of the Furies</span><hr size=1> Alecto sat in her throne decorated in vines with black thorns all around them. Her long maroon strings that hung from her outfit dangled against the chair.<br>
<br>
Megaera sat opposite of her sister. Her wild brown hair tossed back, as she sat in her own throne. Pure black silk with blood stains on the arms.<br>
<br>
Tisiphone lay sprawled out against the fountain in the middle of the Temple. She was gazing into the water watching the little fishies drop instantly as her fingers touched the liquid.<br>
<br>
Alecto then growled lightly under her breath.<br>
&quot;The Furies are being once again used to do the errands of the Olympians.&quot;<br>
<br>
Megaera followed in thought.<br>
&quot;Our brothers and sisters the Titans never treated us with such disrespect.&quot;<br>
<br>
Tisiphone nodded in agreement as she spoke to her sisters knowing no one was in the temple at the moment. Otherwise, they would be in great pain.<br>
&quot;Hera and a few others treat us well, but once again the male egos have gone against us as they think of us lower than they are.&quot;<br>
<br>
Alecto nodded.<br>
&quot;Which is why for the moment, until we have received the respect deserved, the Furies shall torment only those that we wish to. Poseidon can find his own trident.&quot;<br>
<br>
Megaera smirked.<br>
&quot;I never even looked for the stupid thing.&quot;<br>
<br>
Tisiphone nodded.<br>
&quot;Perhaps when they do not have us to push around anymore, they will understand how needed we can be.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen of the Gods</span><br>  Posts: 64<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/4/01 2:55:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=54.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> a reminder appears </span><hr size=1> As the furies become involved in being upset w/ the Olympians a slim peacock feather falls on the floor between them in the temple.  Hera knew they were beginning to feel unappreciated.  And wanted to remind them with this simple act..that she did in fact..care. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/utheerinyes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Erinyes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 52<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/4/01 4:00:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=54.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Feather. . . </span><hr size=1> Tisiphone looked down as the feather fell to the floor. She smiled lightly and picked it up showing her sisters.<br>
<br>
Alecto let a small smile cross her lips for a brief moment.<br>
&quot;Hera has always been a wonderous Goddess. She has found appreciation for most of the Olympians, as well as the Titans and creations of before her.&quot;<br>
<br>
